[Student "S"]
{SOUTH has 13 points but has no bid over 1\D. 
NORTH can make a Takeout Double, so he does.

SOUTH now cue-bids \D to show opening hand strength.

NORTH shows his \H suit, SOUTH doesn't like it. 
SOUTH shows her \S suit, NORTH doesn't like it. 
NORTH shows his \C suit, SOUTH likes it fine, but decides 3NT will be easier than 5\C.}

