[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/overcalls"]
[Student "S"]
{WEST would have had a great opening 1\S bid. But when SOUTH opened 1\S 
in front of him he was hornswaggled. He couldn't bid any other suit, he couldn't bid 1NT 
and he sure couldn't bid \Ss. So he must pass.

And so does everybody else pass.}

